@startuml
title ai-server 调度器核心交互流程（MVP）

actor User
participant "Web 工作台界面" as Web
participant "ai-server HTTP/API" as API
participant "会话路由器" as Router
participant "调度器 Manager" as Orchestrator
database "聊天 Store" as ChatStore
database "调度器 Store" as OStore
participant "PlannerSession\n（Codex 线程）" as Planner
participant "WorkerSession\n（Codex 线程）" as Worker
participant "host-agent" as Host

User -> Web : 提交工作台请求
Web -> API : POST /api/v1/chat/message\n（session kind=workspace）
API -> Router : handleChatMessage(workspace)
Router -> Orchestrator : StartMission(workspaceSessionID, userMessage)
Orchestrator -> OStore : 创建 Mission
Orchestrator -> ChatStore : 创建隐藏的 PlannerSession
Orchestrator -> Planner : thread/start + turn/start\n（PlannerPreset）

Planner -> Orchestrator : 工具调用\norchestrator_dispatch_tasks(tasks)
Orchestrator -> OStore : 校验并入队 TaskRun / HostWorker

loop 在预算内激活 ready hosts
  Orchestrator -> ChatStore : 确保隐藏的 WorkerSession 存在
  Orchestrator -> Host : 执行 "mkdir -p <remotePath>"
  Host --> Orchestrator : 返回 bootstrap 结果
  Orchestrator -> Worker : thread/start + turn/start\n（WorkerPreset）
end

Worker -> Host : 调用 remote execute_* / file ops
Host --> Worker : 输出 / 退出 / 文件结果
Worker --> Orchestrator : turn 事件 / exec 事件 / 回复摘要
Orchestrator -> OStore : 更新 worker / task / relay events
Orchestrator -> ChatStore : Upsert MissionCard / WorkerProgressCard
Orchestrator --> Web : 回推工作台投影视图

alt Worker 发起审批请求
  Worker --> Orchestrator : approval_requested(workerSessionID, approvalID)
  Orchestrator -> OStore : 建立 workspace approval -> worker approval 映射
  Orchestrator -> ChatStore : Upsert WorkerApprovalCard
  Orchestrator --> Web : 回推工作台投影视图
  User -> Web : 通过 / 拒绝
  Web -> API : POST /api/v1/approvals/{id}/decision\n（current session=workspace）
  API -> Router : 解析镜像审批路由
  Router -> Orchestrator : RouteApprovalDecision(...)
  Orchestrator -> Worker : 转发决策到原始 approval
end

alt Planner 或 Worker 请求用户输入
  Planner --> Orchestrator : request_user_input
  Orchestrator -> OStore : 建立 workspace choice -> origin session 映射
  Orchestrator -> ChatStore : Upsert 镜像 ChoiceCard
  Orchestrator --> Web : 回推工作台投影视图
  User -> Web : 填写输入
  Web -> API : POST /api/v1/choices/{id}/answer\n（current session=workspace）
  API -> Router : 解析镜像 choice 路由
  Router -> Orchestrator : RouteChoiceAnswer(...)
  Orchestrator -> Planner : 转发答案
end

alt 用户停止 mission
  User -> Web : 停止 mission
  Web -> API : POST /api/v1/chat/stop\n（session kind=workspace）
  API -> Router : handleChatStop(workspace)
  Router -> Orchestrator : CancelMission(workspaceSessionID)
  Orchestrator -> Worker : turn/interrupt（active workers）
  Orchestrator -> Host : exec/cancel（active remote exec）
  Orchestrator -> OStore : 标记 queued tasks 为 cancelled
  Orchestrator -> ChatStore : 更新 MissionCard
  Orchestrator --> Web : 回推工作台投影视图
end

Worker --> Orchestrator : turn completed / failed / aborted
Orchestrator -> OStore : 释放预算
Orchestrator -> OStore : 选择下一个 ready host
Orchestrator -> ChatStore : Upsert WorkerCompletionCard / MissionCard
Orchestrator --> Web : 回推最终工作台投影视图

User -> Web : 打开主机详情
Web -> ChatStore : 读取投影后的只读详情
User -> Web : 跳转到单机对话
Web -> API : 激活或创建\nsession kind=single_host

@enduml
